# Search index

- Build-time Orama DB → static `/search-index.json`
- Index: posts, tags, series, **listed** tools (`getTools()`)
- Cap body text with `MAX_CONTENT_LENGTH` (2000)
- Client: `Search.svelte` fetch → `load` → local `search`
- After schema/URL changes: rebuild before `npm test`
- New AI tools appear in search automatically when `published && listed`
